text_content: body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 800px; margin: 0px auto; padding: 20px; }.container { border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; }button { padding: 10px 15px; background-color: rgb(76, 175, 80); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; }button:hover { background-color: rgb(69, 160, 73); }input, textarea { width: 100%; padding: 10px; margin: 10px 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); border-radius: 4px; }
